{
  "stem": "11998.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I looked at where my mother was, and I could see that she, with my sister, were in the first row of the women's column that was with the young people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that was a good sign, because I knew that the-- with the young people, that means they're going to be sent to work somewhere.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my father was, of course, with the young people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was with the young, you know, boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But there were no infants, because the-- the young children that are below 5, or before 4, I don't know, they-- they went-- they went with the mother.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They went-- they were with their mothers in that lineup of the older women-- young women with children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so I figured it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I remember it was just-- it was like yesterday I figured that my father's going to go to Germany, my mother and my sister are going to go to Germany to work, and I'll stay here in this Auschwitz, whatever this camp was.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I didn't know the name of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But whatever we were, I was going to stay there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I said I was an electrician.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I can earn my keep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I could do anything that they wanted me to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then, just as we do that, my father's calling me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And so I jump out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he's standing there in front of me with a-- a Nazi soldier.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he says, that's him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He's 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He's an electrician.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he's a good worker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he looks at me and says, he's pretty small for 17.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says-- he says, yeah, but he's a good worker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's worked for a number of years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he thinks and he thinks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, OK, take him, but make it quick.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
